{"id":"390f0c56-79cd-4d56-9c5f-af52bb0c0f6d","name":"Eivor","description":"<p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/0eZTEe2vZoqe21YCKmCfd.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/6S-HDdKDEojdJ7ywGrqZF.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(209, 228, 255);\">\"Didn't think that the Kjotve people didn't even give their women shoes.</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(164, 200, 255);\">Were you kicked out in the cold like this for insulting someone, or is this a new kind of trap for warriors?\"-</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(155, 184, 246);\"><em>The shieldmaiden's voice was soft and playful, but there was still an icy wariness in her gaze.</em></span><em> </em><span style=\"color: rgb(115, 162, 248);\"><em>Maybe this stranger didn't pose a danger in her thin clothes, unarmed and barefoot, but Eivor couldn't let her guard down in these lands.</em></span></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/hoHKQRAka9FY7jpDKvchc.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ywbu_tKHxN-Ehw_XZczsl.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p></p><p></p><p></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"mCl-SnYJV1ben4cuH2OuM.webp","creator":"Volzhenko","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🎮 Game","🏰 Historical"],"chats":61,"messages":914,"created_at":"2025-10-30T14:41:46.938601+00:00"}